<P><IMG height=146 src="/images/partners/Lennon_Bus_150.gif" width=150 align=right>The John Lennon Educational Tour Bus travels year round to bring the latest audio and video technology to schools, youth centers, conferences, festivals, concert tours, battles of the bands and more. <BR><BR>Yoko Ono will unveil a brand new Lennon Bus at the 2008 International CES. Take a tour during show hours and enjoy a daily performance on its stage in the <A href="/attendees/show_floor/areas/concierge.asp">CES Concierge Center </A>from 4-6 p.m.</P>

