<span class="subhead">CES to Host Technology and Engineering Emmy Awards</span>

<br><br><IMG height=80 src="/images/partners/Emmys_07.gif" width=105 align=right>CES will host the Technology &amp; Engineering Emmy Awards for the second year in a row! These awards honor achievements in two areas: Science &amp; Technology for Television - broadcast, cable and satellite distribution and Advanced Media Technology - interactive television, gaming technology and the Internet, cell phones, private networks and personal media players. For ticket and event information, visit the National Television Academy website at <A href="http://www.emmyonline.tv" target=_blank>www.emmyonline.tv</A>.

